attributes.action: illegal enclosure of common land in 18th/19th centuries
attributes.additional_details:
common land is just that--COMMON.  for the use of the PEOPLE.
enclosures of common land was theft from the people of this country, pure and simple.
all land illegally aqired by enclosure acts should be returned to public use--free and unimpeded.
and NO compensation!  THIVES don't get compensation!
